thread.title_full: Test Me DNA reviewed by Ruthie B.

author: Ruthie B.
title: Ruthie B.
text:
Excellent and easy test to take.. I called ordered test over phone, PEOPLE were wonderful.. I received the test very easy to use.. Popped in the mail and I got a call telling me the results. I would suggest it to anyone who would like to know about their DNA..
I was testing with my sister if we had same parents and YES we did so happy to find out the Truth which has haunted me for years..I would recommend company and I found it to be easy. Just wished I would have done it years ago..
